## Task

Parse Fortnite.digest.verse into structured index.

## Digest Format

The digest is Verse source code with all device definitions:

```verse
device_campfire_device = class():
    # Events
    TriggerOnEnterRadius():event(such as {Agent}):void
    TriggerOnExtinguish():event():void
    OnDisabled():event():void

    # Receivers  
    ReceiverAddFuel(Amount:int):void
    EnableWhenReceiving():void

    # Methods
    AddFuel(Amount:int):void
    Extinguish():void
```

## Parser Strategy

Line-based parsing (no tree-sitter needed initially):

```rust
pub struct DigestParser;

impl DigestParser {
    pub fn parse(content: &str) -> Result<DigestIndex> {
        let mut index = DigestIndex::default();
        let mut current_device: Option<String> = None;

        for line in content.lines() {
            let trimmed = line.trim();

            // Device class declaration
            if let Some(name) = Self::parse_device_decl(trimmed) {
                current_device = Some(name.clone());
                index.devices.entry(name).or_default();
                continue;
            }

            // Event declaration
            if let Some(event) = Self::parse_event(trimmed) {
                if let Some(device) = &current_device {
                    index.devices.get_mut(device).unwrap().events.push(event);
                }
            }

            // Method declaration
            if let Some(method) = Self::parse_method(trimmed) {
                if let Some(device) = &current_device {
                    index.devices.get_mut(device).unwrap().methods.push(method);
                }
            }
        }

        Ok(index)
    }

    fn parse_device_decl(line: &str) -> Option<String> {
        // device_campfire_device = class():
        let re = regex!(r"^([a-z_]+_device)\s*=\s*class\(\)\s*:");
        re.captures(line).map(|c| c[1].to_string())
    }

    fn parse_event(line: &str) -> Option<Event> {
        // TriggerOnEnterRadius():event(such as {Agent}):void
        let re = regex!(r"^([A-Za-z]+)\(([^)]*)\)\s*:\s*event\(([^)]*)\)\s*:\s*(\w+)");
        // ...
    }
}
```

