## Struct Handling

Team specs like (TeamType=Any,TeamIndex=1) are StructProperty:

```rust
fn format_struct(s: &StructPropertyData) -> String {
    let mut parts = vec![];
    for prop in &s.value.properties {
        let key = prop.get_name().get_owned_content();
        if let Some(val) = property_to_string(prop) {
            parts.push(format!("{}={}", key, val));
        }
    }
    format!("({})", parts.join(","))
}
